Well here is my second deathrun. I hope you enjoy it.

FIXED - Updated, fixed sound bugs and added spawns
FIXED2 - Fixed sound bug again and changed buttons

--------------------------------------------------------

- 3 Terrorist Spawns
- 48 Counter Terrorist Spawns
- 12 Player Controlled Traps
- 2 Non Player Controlled Traps
- The most over the top afk killer yet!

--------------------------------------------------------

Run Down:

The Terrorists have made an assualt on the counter terrorists base and the battle has been going on for a while. The terrorists manage to get past the cts and get to the control panels. The terrorists push forward and the cts have no choice but to retreat and make there way back up to the control rooms.

Watch out for deadly snipers at spawn

--------------------------------------------------------
Once again, this map didnt go exactly how i planned. But oh well.
